>.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"klip-hiw__tagline\">\n          ✨ That's it — four seconds, zero fuss.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  /* ===== WRAPPER ===== */\n  .klip-hiw {\n    margin: 8px 0 8px;\n    padding: 28px 20px;\n    background: #fdf8f5;\n    border: 1px solid #f0e8e0;\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    font-family: inherit;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__inner {\n    max-width: 640px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* ===== TITRE ===== */\n  .klip-hiw__title {\n    font-size: 1.75rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1c1c1c;\n    margin: 0 0 22px 0;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n  }\n\n  /* ===== LAYOUT ===== */\n  .klip-hiw__layout {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 24px;\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n\n  /* ===== VIDÉO ===== */\n  .klip-hiw__video-wrap {\n    flex: 0 0 auto;\n    width: 185px;\n    border-radius: 14px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n    background: #000;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__video {\n    display: block;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 330px;\n    object-fit: cover;\n  }\n\n  /* ===== ÉTAPES ===== */\n  .klip-hiw__steps {\n    flex: 1;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 0;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__step {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    padding: 12px 0;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__step-number {\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    width: 30px;\n    height: 30px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #e8a89c;\n    color: #fff;\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__step-content {\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__step-text {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n\n  .klip-hiw__step-text strong {\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #1c1c1c;\n  }\n\n  /* ===== SÉPARATEURS ===== */\n  .klip-hiw__divider {\n    height: 1px;\n    background: #f0e8e0