    "faq_6HBHkM": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_6WhXFW": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does VELVY™ work on all hair types?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. VELVY™ is designed for fine, thick, straight, curly or textured hair. The flat magnetic system closes firmly around your hair without slipping or squeezing too tight. Simply adjust how much hair you take in the clip — a smaller section for very thick hair, a slightly larger one for fine hair.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_VbbtCC": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it comfortable to wear all day?",
            "content": "<p>VELVY™ is designed to be completely forgotten. Its flat shape creates no bump or pressure point at the back of your head — you can lean back, drive, work, exercise or lie down without any discomfort. Because there's no spring crushing your hair, there's no continuous pressure building up to give you a headache either.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_KQKJJF": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is VELVY™ safer than a regular clip in the car?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, and that's one of its biggest advantages. Bulky clips create a rigid \"spike\" between your skull and the headrest. In the event of sudden braking or a collision, that hard point can press into your head. VELVY™ stays flat against the headrest — no protruding bump, no bulky metal piece at the back of your skull. You keep your hair up, with a far more reassuring accessory on the road.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_ebV7BW": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will VELVY™ damage or break my hair?",
            "content": "<p>Not at all. VELVY™ has no aggressive teeth or spring that can snag and pull at your hair. The hold works through gentle magnetic pressure, with no harsh tugging. The result: less breakage, fewer hairs left behind in the clip, and no marks when you take it out — even with daily use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_UPwiW4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is VELVY™ genuinely durable?",
            "content": "<p>VELVY™ is not a disposable clip. With no fragile spring, there's nothing to bend, snap or dislodge. The magnetic system handles repeated opening and closing, drops on the floor and life at the bottom of a handbag. As long as you're not forcing it, you'll keep the same hold strength and shape for a long time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_tfq4jP": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are the magnets safe for everyday use?",
            "content": "<p>VELVY™'s magnets are small and fully integrated into the structure, away from your skin and scalp. They have no impact on your health and won't damage your hair. You can wear VELVY™ next to your phone, your bank card or on a plane without any issue — it's designed for everyday use, just like any other modern hair accessory.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
